flowchart TD
    Start([Start Quick Sort]) --> GetList[Get Employee List to Sort]
    GetList --> CheckSize{list.size > 1}
    CheckSize -->|No| ReturnList[Return list already sorted]
    ReturnList --> End([End Sort])

    CheckSize -->|Yes| CallQuickSort[Call quickSortHelper low=0, high=size-1]
    CallQuickSort --> CheckBounds{low < high}

    CheckBounds -->|Yes| Partition[Call partition low, high]
    Partition --> ChoosePivot[Choose pivot = list.get high]
    ChoosePivot --> InitI[i = low - 1]
    InitI --> InitJ[j = low]

    InitJ --> LoopJ{j < high}
    LoopJ -->|Yes| CompareJPivot{list.get j .name <= pivot.name}

    CompareJPivot -->|Yes| IncrementI[i++]
    IncrementI --> Swap1[Swap list.get i with list.get j]
    Swap1 --> NextJ[j++]

    CompareJPivot -->|No| NextJ
    NextJ --> LoopJ

    LoopJ -->|No| FinalSwap[Swap list.get i+1 with list.get high]
    FinalSwap --> ReturnPivot[Return pivotIndex = i + 1]

    ReturnPivot --> RecurseLeft[Recursively sort LEFT:<br/>quickSortHelper low, pivotIndex-1]
    RecurseLeft --> RecurseRight[Recursively sort RIGHT:<br/>quickSortHelper pivotIndex+1, high]
    RecurseRight --> CheckBounds

    CheckBounds -->|No| DoneRecursion[Recursion Complete]
    DoneRecursion --> DisplayTime[Display: Completed in X ms]
    DisplayTime --> End

